<item>
            <title>[DATAMONGO-1236] MongoOperations findAndModify and updateFirst do not include the _class in Map values</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAMONGO-1236</link>
                <project id="10701" key="DATAMONGO">Spring Data MongoDB</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a map of type LinkedHashMap&amp;lt;String, Object&amp;gt;  is updated via MongoOperations findAndModify or updateFirst, the _class field is not saved for the map values.  Therefore, later reads of the data do not convert the value to the correct type, instead leaving it as LinkedHashMap. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please see attached maven project for test illustrating the problem. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Java Runtime 1.8.0_45-b14, mongo 3.0.2 </environment>
